## 11. Checklist per Module

When migrating each module `xxx`:

- [ ] Create `src/xxx.rs`
- [ ] Replace `#include "yyy.h"` with `pub use crate::yyy::*` or `use crate::yyy::*`
- [ ] Convert macro constants to `const`/`static` with `// Original: #define MACRO`
- [ ] Convert macro functions to Rust functions with `// This was a macro`
- [ ] Define `XxxState` struct
- [ ] Add state fields for all globals from `xxx.c` with `// Original: varname`
- [ ] Add placeholder functions for extern variables from other modules with `todo!()`
- [ ] Convert each function to a method on `XxxState` with `// Original: FunctionName`
- [ ] Use `&self` for all methods (never `&mut self`); use `RefCell` for mutable fields

